Let A[1.. n] be an array of n distinct numbers. If i < j and A[i] > A[j],
then the pair (i, j) is called an inversion of A. Give an algorithm and
develop the program that determines the number of inversions in any
permutation on n elements in Θ(nlgn) worst-case time. (CLRS
Problems 2-4 & Hint: Modify merge sort.)

在陣列中尋找逆序對的數量。
(逆序對:在陣列排前面的數字 大於排後面的數字者)

input:
5
20
31
82
64
17



output:
5



因為
20 > 17
31 > 17
82 > 64
82 > 17
64 > 17
所以output為5
